SOL>>
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Step1:

      goto->> Gradle Scripts>build.gradle and check for 
          dependencies {
          classpath 'com.android.tools.build:gradle:3.0.1'    //update gradle value (ex: 3.0.1 to  x.x.x)
Step2:        
      goto->> Gradle Scripts>gradle-wrapper.properties(Gradle version) and check for
      distributionUrl=https\://services.gradle.org/distributions/gradle-4.1-all.zip     //update gradle value (ex: 4.1 to  x.x)
Step3:      
      Goto message box>
      Click on Re-Download dependencies and sync project(network Required)
Step4:
      "ReBuild Project" or "Make Project" in Build Menu.
Step5:
      Run the App.
      
      
